### Get All Taxes
GET http://localhost:8081/api/taxes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Active Taxes Only
GET http://localhost:8081/api/taxes/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Tax by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/taxes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Tax - PPh 21%
POST http://localhost:8081/api/taxes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "PPh 21%",
  "percentage": 21.00,
  "description": "Pajak Penghasilan 21%",
  "isActive": true
}

